ext.1/packages/core/src/zone/ng_zone.ts#L186-L191\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.2.0-next.1/packages/core/src/zone/ng_zone.ts#L192-L215\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.2.0-next.1/packages/core/src/zone/ng_zone.ts#L216-L245\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.2.0-next.1/packages/core/src/zone/ng_zone.ts#L246-L256\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.2.0-next.1/packages/core/src/zone/ng_zone.ts#L257-L281\n-->"
